{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"## S5 implemented + verified LIVE — 2026-06-30 (commit dd36a3750)\n\nReplication plugin (bundled) configured + deploy key live. navabpc/rebar main UNCHANGED at cea18e2 throughout (no real-main advance — that is S7's e2e).\n\n**AC verification (subagent + alarm test, all PASS):**\n- AC1 — Replication push works: replication_log shows `Push to ...rebar.git ... refs/heads/main:refs/heads/main force=no ... 0 retries`; a tag pushed to Gerrit replicated to GitHub (`git ls-remote` showed gerrit-repl-smoke=cea18e2), then deleted from both (cleanup confirmed).\n- AC2 — projects=rebar binding: only `rebar` replicates (config + log show only `rebar:` scheduling).\n- AC3 — refs/changes/* + refs/meta/config NOT pushed: `git ls-remote github | grep refs/changes|refs/meta` empty.\n- AC4 — mirror=false, replicationMaxRetries=3, timeout=60.\n- AC5 — `[replication] eventsDirectory=data/replication`; /var/gerrit/data/replication exists (crash-safe queue).\n- AC6 — NON-FORCE enforced: forced Gerrit main to a divergent root; replication returned `REJECTED_NONFASTFORWARD`; **GitHub main stayed cea18e2 (unchanged)**. Gerrit main restored.\n- AC7 — deploy key on disk: /var/gerrit/.ssh/id_ed25519 mode 0600 owner uid 1000; ~/.ssh/config routes github.com to it.\n- AC8 — fail-closed: materialize-deploy-key.sh with a bogus SSM param exits non-zero (ParameterNotFound), writes no key.\n- AC9 — `ssh -T git@github.com` (as gerrit user) -> \"Hi navapbc/rebar! You've successfully authenticated\".\n- AC10 — reproducible as-code: register-deploy-key.sh + materialize-deploy-key.sh + setup-replication.sh + replication.config (idempotent).\n- AC11 — replication-failure ALERT fires: CloudWatch alarm `rebar-gerrit-replication-errors` on `rebar/host:replication_errors`; the observability probe detected the AC6 non-FF line and published the metric -> alarm transitioned OK -> ALARM (verified); recovered to OK after a 0 datapoint.\n- AC12 — kill-switch <5min: `mv replication.config aside` + restart -> \"not replicating\"; restored -> \"Succeeded! (OK)\".\n- ADR-0010 committed (one-way-door contract, BSL note, rotation, kill-switch).\n\n**Deploy key:** registered on navapbc/rebar (write-enabled, id 155914477), private key from SSM /rebar/prod/github-replication-deploy-key.\n**NOTE for S7:** admin cannot direct-push to refs/heads/main (review-gated, by design) — the real-main advance e2e must go through the review/submit flow (or a deliberate temp ACL).\n\n**Code review (subagent):** VERDICT was CHANGES-REQUESTED for 1 blocker — observability.sh `grep -c || echo 0` corrupted the count on the healthy zero-failure path. FIXED (drop `|| echo 0`, `total=${total:-0}`); redeployed + verified clean (total=1 single line, new=0, publishes 0). NITs (ssh-keyscan TOFU; dimension-contract comment) addressed/noted."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782793375025816001,"uuid":"819a980f-f904-4b14-bd04-7a986817b5e2"}